#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"​Once validated, one or more return orders are automatically created in the "
"<b>Return App</b>. If you handle different rental periods (like 7 days for "
"board games and 21 days for books), Odoo will create a separate return order "
"for each distinct rental period."
msgstr ""
